Install:
1. make
2. sudo make install
3. sudo su postgres -c 'psql -d DBNAME -f /usr/share/postgresql/PGVERSION/contrib/pg_strmatch_install.sql'
4. Run test (optional): sudo su postgres -c 'psql -d DBNAME -f test.sql'

Uninstall:
1. sudo su postgres -c 'psql -d DBNAME -f pg_strmatch_uninstall.sql'

Usage:
psql=# SELECT remove_spaces(' no  more spaces ');
remove_spaces  
----------------
 no more spaces
 (1 row)
